{"tid":2325783,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"配合疫情追蹤需要   Apple 向舊 iPhone 推出 iOS 12.5 更新","createTime":"2020-12-15T00:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:52.000Z","uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c417c66a5f825717301f6f09bda07f4b4b54fa3","tid":2325783,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:50:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/15/apple-ios12-5-old-iphone-covid-19/software/ios-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F15%2Fapple-ios12-5-old-iphone-covid-19%2Fsoftware%2Fios-app%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=aac8f5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/15/apple-ios12-5-old-iphone-covid-19/software/ios-app/</a><br />\n為了防疫的需要，歐美不少國家都利用手機追蹤程式，一旦有人不幸感染武漢肺炎，就會利用儲存於手機的資料，找出與確診者有接觸的人。大部份歐美國家都採用 Apple 和 Google 合作開發的 Exposure Notification API，而且個介面早前已經支援型號較新的手機。<br />\n<br />\n昨日 Apple 宣佈為一系列無法升級 iOS 14 的舊手機，例如 iPhone 6 系列等，提供 iOS 12.5 系統更新。雖然 Apple 已經有一段時間沒有更新 iOS 12，但今次是特別針對仍然使用舊機的用戶，讓他們同樣受到保護，同時提升整體社會的防疫能力，所以特別將武漢肺炎通知系統加入，讓用戶自行選擇是否使用。"},{"pid":"f5bd9140dbaf117895e595c785cba4dba34945e7","tid":2325783,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n<br />\n平時迫人換機<br />\n<br />\n邊有咁好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那cook"},{"pid":"9f56ed476e64ae62fa7e4d605a251e1b43ae82be","tid":2325783,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:55:35.000Z","msg":"疫苗都出 而家先訓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009a3a9de2ff86beb064770e0b051502493a7f22","tid":2325783,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5bd9140dbaf117895e595c785cba4dba34945e7","tid":2325783,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n<br />\n平時迫人換機<br />\n<br />\n邊有咁好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那cook"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:57:32.000Z","msg":"啲人揾借口換姐<br />\n利申仲撚緊7"},{"pid":"e6bbd245f00b483cc499188fff4263d7968e5ed2","tid":2325783,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"xx-large\">安心出行</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}